snippet.title: Kissy Cutie the Trailer
snippet.description:
Kissy Cutie - a visual novel
This free unofficial  Undertale fan game will be released July 2019!

Many thanks to all the fans who contributed their time and talent to this massive project of love!

Many many things have been improved upon and redesigned since the demo was released almost two years ago.

You can find the website + game demo here -
https://xocolatl-games.itch.io/undertale-kc

KC will be available on PC, Android, and hopefully IOS.

Subscribe to Xocolatl Games to follow our other games in progress!
